{"tid":1562312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"爆眼少女遭恐嚇滋擾 身心壓力大親友曾擬組自衛隊","createTime":"2019-09-12T03:22:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T10:21:12.000Z","uid":68738,"like":210,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"85e1a6ffce8b7e94b7fb2f893ad54217418455e3","tid":1562312,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"警察在8.11聲稱為「保衞」尖沙嘴警署，疑瞄準少女頭部開槍射布袋彈，打爆其眼球恐失明和毀容。惟警方至今仍未交代其發射的布袋彈是否與少女傷勢有關，更無視少女的律師信，日前（9日）表明已利用法庭搜查令，從醫管局取得少女的醫療報告。「爆眼少女」的朋友再以「人生玩&times;員」賬號在連登討論區發帖，指少女自拍片報平安後，遭受各種滋擾、恐嚇及咒罵，害怕「被自殺」，亦曾想過親友自組自衛隊，指少女傷勢未愈，又要擔心自己及親友人身安全，加上不停睇醫生及律師，他們的身體及精神壓力非常大，但細節不便透露。<br />\n<br />\n少女朋友早前曾稱，由於警方拒絕提供法庭搜查令等資料，已提呈司法覆核，少女的代表律師亦已向警方及醫管局發律師信，反對醫管局向警方交出其醫療紀錄。對於警方以醫療報告擁有者是醫管局，指不存在向「第三者」交代手令情況，少女朋友不滿警方無視反對，無理索取醫療報告，更將屬當事人的爆眼少女稱呼為「第三者」。她又再提到律師已前後出了4封信件要求警方提供法庭手令編號，但完全未獲回覆，「直情 I don&rsquo;t give a fxckxck」。她更說甚至連她們亦未拿到有關報告，對警方得悉的報告資料完全無從得知，亦不滿警方可胡亂索取病人私隱，「今日佢可以無理拎我地報告，先例一開，他日佢都可以無理由咁拎大家既報告」，形容為正式與內地接軌。<br />\n<br />\n少女朋友亦提到少女剛受傷後一星期，整日大部份時間都在不清醒的狀態，痛楚令她不能睜開眼睛，更會頭痛頭暈，甚至「暈到嘔」，卻同時要擔心警方做法。她炮轟政府不停欺壓一個受傷無助小市民，強調少女現時最重要應是休養及專注佢眼睛復原，現時卻要四處奔波及煩惱，「但大家可以放心，家姐話佢係唔會被擊倒，只要香港人一日堅持，佢一日都會企出黎（嚟），為自己嘅權利同正義發聲，佢會永遠企係（喺）雞蛋嘅一面」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190912/60035995?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190912%2F60035995%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=duP9xtlDTMOxgFFwFRXy%2FTbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=851eed28\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190912%2F60035995%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=6ffe884e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190912/60035995?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"655e7e3f2e8689bebe8fa23c333402777213cc39","tid":1562312,"uid":61257,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:23:30.000Z","msg":"CLS 死支狗"},{"pid":"37a6020342760d52578b76a2bde2e9380c116b58","tid":1562312,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f3ad3eade474d85465faf1502c758644a40d6fe2","tid":1562312,"uid":8410,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"睇黎班狗成日搞佢， 真係痴撚線， 同新疆無分別"},{"pid":"1d3d9d0c549396d31368db9111325ee00399bd6f","tid":1562312,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f65befea7dadf9acfa6d898985dd69e8c522ee2","tid":1562312,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"85e1a6ffce8b7e94b7fb2f893ad54217418455e3","tid":1562312,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T03:22:42.000Z","msg":"警察在8.11聲稱為「保衞」尖沙嘴警署，疑瞄準少女頭部開槍射布袋彈，打爆其眼球恐失明和毀容。惟警